g=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἑλιχθέντων ὑπ᾽ Ἀχαιῶν</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">when</tr_> they <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">turned to face</tr_> the foe, ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:74\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">74</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:408\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">408</biblScope> </bibl>; so of a wild boar, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἑλιξάμενος</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">having turned to bay</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:17:283\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.283</biblScope> </bibl>; of a serpent, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">coil himself</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἑλισσόμενος περὶ χειῇ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:95\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.95</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἡ δέ τ᾽ ἐλισσομένη πέτεται</foreign> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">καλαῦροψ</foreign>) the shepherd's staff flies <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">spinning through the air</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:23:846\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.846</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κνίση . . ἑλισσομένη περὶ καπνῷ</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">rolling</tr_> with the smoke, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:317\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.317</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἑλισσόμενοι περὶ δίνας</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">whirled round</tr_> in the eddies, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:11